<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Portfolio — Baptiste Barrachina</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,300;0,8..60,400;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,300;1,8..60,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══════════════════ VARIABLES ═══════════════════ */
:root {
  --navy:  #1B2A4A;
  --teal:  #0D7A72;
  --coral: #C94F3A;
  --ink:   #1C1C1C;
  --mid:   #5A6270;
  --light: #EEF2F5;
  --rule:  #C8D4DC;
  --page:  #FAFAF8;
  --cream: #F3EFE8;
}
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { font-size: 17px; }

/* ═══════════════════ BODY ═══════════════════ */
body {
  font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ink);
  background: #D8D4CC;
  min-height: 100vh;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

/* ═══════════════════ TABS NAV ═══════════════════ */
.tab-nav {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 200;
  background: var(--navy);
  display: flex; align-items: stretch;
  padding: 0 2rem;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
}
.tab-nav-brand {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  padding-right: 2rem;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  margin-right: 1rem; white-space: nowrap;
}
.tab-nav-brand span { color: var(--teal); margin-left: 0.3rem; }
.tab-btn {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #7A9BB5; background: none; border: none;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0.85rem;
  cursor: pointer; transition: color .2s, border-color .2s;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.45rem; white-space: nowrap;
}
.tab-btn:hover { color: #AACCE0; }
.tab-btn.active { color: #fff; border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }

/* ═══════════════════ PANELS ═══════════════════ */
.tab-panel { display: none; padding: 2.5rem 1rem 5rem; }
.tab-panel.active { display: block; }

/* ═══════════════════ PAGE WRAPPER ═══════════════════ */
.page {
  max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
  background: var(--page);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.18), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* ═══════════════════ COVER ═══════════════════ */
.cover {
  background: var(--navy);
  padding: 4rem 4rem 3.5rem;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.cover::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
  width: 220px; height: 100%; background: var(--teal); opacity: 0.18;
}
.cover-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--teal);
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.cover h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 0.15em;
}
.cover h1 span { color: var(--teal); display: block; }
.cover-sub {
  font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
  color: #8BAFC4; margin-top: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.cover-meta {
  display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); padding-top: 1.5rem;
}
.cover-meta-item { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #6E90A8; }
.cover-meta-item strong { display: block; color: #AACCE0; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }

/* ═══════════════════ TOC ═══════════════════ */
.toc { background: var(--cream); border-left: 4px solid var(--teal); padding: 2.5rem 4rem; }
.toc-title {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.toc ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: toc; }
.toc ol li {
  counter-increment: toc;
  display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule);
  font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--navy);
}
.toc ol li::before {
  content: counter(toc, decimal-leading-zero);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--teal); min-width: 1.8rem;
}
.toc ol li .dots { flex: 1; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule); margin: 0 0.3rem; height: 1em; }
.toc ol li .pg { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--mid); }

/* ═══════════════════ CONTENT ═══════════════════ */
.content { padding: 0 4rem; }
.section { padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.section:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 4rem; }
.section-header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.section-num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--teal); letter-spacing: 0.1em; min-width: 2rem; }
.section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.15; }
.subsection { margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
.subsection-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--coral); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; padding-bottom: 0.3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #E8D4CF; }

p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.97rem; color: #2C2C2C; }
p + p { text-indent: 1.5em; }
p:first-of-type { text-indent: 0; }

.pull-quote {
  margin: 2rem 0; padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); background: var(--light);
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ═══════════════════ SAE BLOCK — toujours 3 colonnes ═══════════════════ */
.sae-block { margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: #FCFCFB; }
.sae-header {
  background: var(--navy); padding: 0.8rem 1.25rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
}
.sae-level {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--teal); background: rgba(13,122,114,0.2); padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.sae-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; color: #fff; flex: 1; }
.sae-tools { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; color: #5E8499; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

/* Grille TOUJOURS 3 colonnes égales */
.sae-body {
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.sae-col-title {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.sae-col p { font-size: 0.87rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; text-indent: 0 !important; }
.sae-col ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
.sae-col ul li { font-size: 0.87rem; padding: 0.15rem 0 0.15rem 1rem; position: relative; color: #2C2C2C; }
.sae-col ul li::before { content: '›'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--teal); font-weight: 600; }

/* Note bilan pleine largeur sous les 3 colonnes */
.result-note {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  background: var(--cream); padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
  font-size: 0.83rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--mid);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.result-note strong { color: var(--navy); font-style: normal; }

/* ═══════════════════ SKILL / STAT / TIMELINE / FOOTER ═══════════════════ */
.skill-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
.skill-cat-title {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.3rem; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy);
}
.skill-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.skill-name { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--ink); min-width: 130px; }
.skill-bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 4px; background: var(--rule); }
.skill-bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--teal); }

.stat-row { display: flex; margin: 1.5rem 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.stat-item { flex: 1; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.stat-val { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--teal); line-height: 1; }
.stat-val.coral { color: var(--coral); }
.stat-val.navy  { color: var(--navy); }
.stat-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--mid); margin-top: 0.25rem; font-style: italic; }

.contact-block {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.3rem 2rem;
  margin: 1.25rem 0; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--light); border-left: 3px solid var(--navy);
}
.contact-item { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--ink); padding: 0.2rem 0; }
.contact-item .label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--mid);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; display: block; text-transform: uppercase;
}

.timeline { margin: 1.25rem 0; position: relative; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
.timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0.4rem; top: 0.4rem; bottom: 0.4rem; width: 1px; background: var(--rule); }
.timeline-item { margin-bottom: 0.9rem; position: relative; }
.timeline-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -1.1rem; top: 0.45rem; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); border: 2px solid var(--page); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--teal); }
.timeline-date { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--teal); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
.timeline-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); }
.timeline-text em { color: var(--mid); font-style: normal; font-size: 0.83rem; }

.evolution-note {
  background: rgba(13,122,114,0.06); border: 1px dashed var(--teal);
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem; font-size: 0.87rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--teal); margin-top: 1rem;
}
.evolution-note strong { font-style: normal; color: var(--navy); }

.doc-footer {
  background: var(--navy); padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
.doc-footer-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #fff; }
.doc-footer-info { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #5E8499; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-align: right; }

/* ═══════════════════ CV TAB — styles Bootstrap natifs préservés ═══════════════════ */
#tab-cv .content-cv {
  max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
  background: #fff; padding: 2rem;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}
#tab-cv h1 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 2rem; }
#tab-cv .subtitle { color: #c0392b; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
#tab-cv .contact-info li { background: #ecf0f1; font-size: 0.88rem; }
#tab-cv .photo-profil img { width: 130px; height: 130px; object-fit: cover; border-color: #2c3e50 !important; }
#tab-cv h2 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 1.15rem; border-bottom-color: #c0392b !important; }
#tab-cv h3 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 1rem; }
#tab-cv th { background: #f8f9fa; color: #2c3e50; font-size: 0.87rem; }
#tab-cv td { font-size: 0.87rem; }
#tab-cv td:first-child { color: #c0392b; }
#tab-cv .skill-list li { border-left-color: #2c3e50 !important; font-size: 0.87rem; }

/* ═══════════════════ DOCS TAB ═══════════════════ */
.docs-page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
.docs-header { background: var(--navy); padding: 2.5rem 3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.docs-header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #fff; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.docs-header p { color: #7A9BB5; font-size: 0.9rem; font-style: italic; }

.doc-card { background: var(--page); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
.doc-card-header { background: var(--navy); padding: 1rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
.doc-card-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--teal); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.doc-card-icon.pdf  { background: var(--coral); }
.doc-card-icon.pptx { background: #B7472A; }
.doc-card-icon.html { background: #E44D26; }
.doc-card-title-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.doc-card-title { color: #fff; font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
.doc-card-type { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; color: #5E8499; }
.doc-card-body { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
.doc-card-body p { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; color: #2C2C2C; text-indent: 0 !important; }
.doc-card-meta { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0.75rem 0; }
.doc-meta-tag { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; background: var(--light); color: var(--navy); padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--rule); }

/* iframe viewer */
.doc-viewer-toggle { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.doc-viewer-btn {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: var(--navy); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 0.45rem 1rem; cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .2s;
}
.doc-viewer-btn:hover { background: var(--teal); }
.doc-viewer-note { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--mid); font-style: italic; }
.doc-iframe-wrap { display: none; margin-top: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--rule); }
.doc-iframe-wrap.open { display: block; }
.doc-iframe-wrap iframe { width: 100%; height: 640px; border: none; background: #f5f5f5; display: block; }
.doc-iframe-toolbar {
  background: var(--navy); padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
.doc-iframe-toolbar span { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #5E8499; }
.doc-iframe-close { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--teal); background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
.doc-iframe-close:hover { color: #fff; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ NAVIGATION ══ -->
<nav class="tab-nav">
  <div class="tab-nav-brand">Baptiste<span>Barrachina</span></div>
  <button class="tab-btn active"  onclick="switchTab('portfolio',this)">Portfolio</button>
  <button class="tab-btn"        onclick="switchTab('cv',this)">CV</button>
  <button class="tab-btn"        onclick="switchTab('docs',this)">Documents &amp; Rapports</button>
</nav>


<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     ONGLET 1 — PORTFOLIO
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="tab-portfolio" class="tab-panel active">
<div class="page">

  <div class="cover">
    <div class="cover-label">Portfolio de Compétences · BUT Science des Données</div>
    <h1>Baptiste<span>Barrachina</span></h1>
    <p class="cover-sub">Étudiant en deuxième année — IUT d'Avignon · 2024–2026</p>
    <div class="cover-meta">
      <div class="cover-meta-item"><strong>Formation</strong>BUT Science des Données</div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item"><strong>Établissement</strong>IUT d'Avignon</div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item"><strong>Parcours</strong>EMS</div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item"><strong>Année</strong>2025–2026</div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item"><strong>Contact</strong>barrachinabaptiste@gmail.com</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="toc">
    <div class="toc-title">Table des matières</div>
    <ol>
      <li>Présentation de la formation <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">I</span></li>
      <li>Traiter — deux projets <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">II</span></li>
      <li>Analyser — deux projets <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">III</span></li>
      <li>Valoriser — deux projets <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">IV</span></li>
      <li>Modéliser — projet optionnel <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">V</span></li>
      <li>Compétences transversales et numériques <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">VI</span></li>
      <li>Passions et engagements <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">VII</span></li>
      <li>Conclusion <span class="dots"></span><span class="pg">VIII</span></li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <!-- II — FORMATION -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">I</span><h2 class="section-title">Présentation de la formation</h2></div>
      <p>Le BUT Science des données est un bachelor universitaire de technologie de trois ans (bac+3) dispensé à l'IUT d'Avignon. Il forme des professionnels capables de collecter, traiter, analyser et valoriser des données dans des contextes variés — entreprises privées, collectivités, organismes publics ou associations.</p>
      <div class="subsection"><div class="subsection-title">Structure et durée</div></div>
      <p>La formation repose sur une alternance de cours magistraux, travaux dirigés en salle informatique, projets en groupe et stage en entreprise dès la deuxième année. Les étudiants travaillent sur des données réelles issues de sources ouvertes (INSEE, data.gouv.fr, etc.).</p>
      <div class="subsection"><div class="subsection-title">Les compétences du référentiel</div></div>
      <p>Le programme est structuré autour de cinq compétences : <em>Traiter</em> (informatique, bases de données), <em>Analyser</em> (mathématiques, statistiques), <em>Valoriser</em> (économie, communication), et deux options — <em>Modéliser</em> ou <em>Développer</em>. Le parcours EMS a pour compétence optionnelle <em>Modéliser</em>.</p>
      <div class="subsection"><div class="subsection-title">Pourquoi cette formation ?</div></div>
      <p>Ce BUT répondait à mes deux attirances : les mathématiques et l'informatique, réunis au service de la donnée. La proximité de l'IUT d'Avignon avec les acteurs économiques locaux — dont le Conseil Départemental du Vaucluse où j'effectue mon stage — en fait un cadre particulièrement formateur.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- III — TRAITER -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">II</span><h2 class="section-title">Traiter</h2></div>
      <p>La compétence Traiter regroupe l'ensemble des savoir-faire liés à la manipulation informatique des données : bases de données relationnelles, langages de requête, outils de reporting, et aujourd'hui technologies web.</p>

      <div class="subsection"><div class="subsection-title">Niveau 1 — SAÉ Reporting à partir de données stockées dans un SGBD</div></div>
      <div class="sae-block">
        <div class="sae-header">
          <span class="sae-level">Niveau 1</span>
          <span class="sae-title">Reporting SGBD · Comportements d'achats des ménages en Rhône-Alpes-Auvergne</span>
          <span class="sae-tools">SQL · pgAdmin · LibreOffice Calc</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sae-body">
          <div class="sae-col">
            <div class="sae-col-title">Contexte</div>
            <p>Exploiter une base de données réelle sur les comportements d'achats des ménages. La question assignée à notre groupe était <strong>« Où ? »</strong> — analyser la dimension géographique des achats dans la région Rhône-Alpes-Auvergne.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sae-col">
            <div class="sae-col-title">Ce que nous avons réalisé</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Extraction des données en SQL (pgAdmin) selon notre thématique</li>
              <li>Export et traitement dans LibreOffice Calc</li>
              <li>Fonctions SI, NB.VAL, SOMMEPROD, EUROCONVERT</li>
              <li>Tableaux croisés dynamiques et graphiques (camembert, bâtons)</li>
              <li>Rédaction d'un rapport structuré et lisible</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="sae-col">
            <div class="sae-col-title">Bilan</div>
            <p>Note dans la médiane de la promotion. Les graphiques et fonctions tableur ont été bien réalisés. Axe d'amélioration : mieux expliquer dans le rapport les formules utilisées et leur justification méthodologique.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-note"><strong>Ce que j'en retiens :</strong> travailler avec un SGBD réel m'a appris à apprivoiser des données imparfaites. La patience et la rigueur dans la phase d'extraction sont aussi importantes que la qualité des graphiques finaux.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection"><div class="subsection-title">Niveau 2 — Technologies Web : création d'un CV en HTML/CSS</div></div>
      <div class="sae-block">
        <div class="sae-header">
          <span class="sae-level">Niveau 2</span>
          <span class="sae-title">Technologies Web (I-E05-3593) · Création d'un CV personnel en HTML et CSS</span>
          <span class="sae-tools">HTML5 · CSS3 · Bootstrap</span>
        </div>
